gate: OPEN
task: S03-T2
title: Port totem-view glass buttons and cards
objective: Incorporate the glass system UI patterns from totem-view into kvit-tracking.

context:
- totem-view contains an excellent glass styling system for buttons and cards (e.g. S05-T4-GlassButtonsAndCards.pd).
- We need to import the CSS classes (backdrop-filter, semi-transparent backgrounds, hover glows) into kvit-tracking to elevate the UI's modern feel.

steps:
1. Locate the glass button and glass card CSS styles/components in `totem-view`.
2. Port these specific styles (base + hover glow, optional variants) into the `kvit-tracking` styling context.
3. Update key buttons and container cards in `kvit-tracking` to utilize these newly imported glass components/classes.

acceptance-criteria:
- [x] Glass button styles and card styles are available and used in kvit-tracking.
- [x] The visual presentation matches the aesthetic defined in the totem-view glass UI system.
